  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_60",
    "english": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies.",
    "japanese": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies.",
    "korean": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies.",
    "spanish": "Demon, a high-ranking Oni warrior. He is one of the executives of \"Kibushu\", a criminal syndicate in Tokyo Kingdom. Despite his frightening face bearing sharp teeth, he is fiercely loyal to his lord, Rakshasa, and displays a courteous demeanor, even using honorifics when speaking to his enemies.\n\nHe practices the quick draw technique, \"Teppeki Kiryu,\" using swift moves to deflect all sorts of attacks. Additionally, his bamboo hat is equipped with a special sensor that allows him to detect the distance between him and his enemies."
  },
